title: Group Therapy: She Was Watching WHAT On Her iPad?
description: "Sienna" calls in because she had an accident with her iPad and now she's concerned when she takes it into Apple that they're going to see the most recent thing she was watching on it.  Will they see it and is there anything she can do about it?
